node.text: Victoria gets REAL with me about her experience with binge eating, body image, and how being a college athlete can take a toll on your mental health. We talk about how she dealt with these challenges and her pathway to therapy and the help we all need from time to time. We end with some tips for performing under pressure, so you don’t want to miss that! My hope is that you all walk away with something that will help you improve your own mental health and remember you are NEVER alone!

node.title: Body Image, Mental Health & More with Victoria Garrick!

node.text: I had a little time on my hands today so I scrolled through my camera roll and threw together this video🤗 Grateful for all these times and these humans and can’t wait to make more memories! ❤️ @alixklineman @jenniferkessy & * @fiapogtenius we need some video with you! 🙈

Can always count on partner-to-coach @jenniferkessy for a balance of intensity and lightheartedness, to tell it like it is, and of course entertain us in the process 🤣 Grateful to have her on our team! 🙏🏼🙌🏼❤️ Enjoy this look at what goes on in our player box during a big match 👊🏼 (also don’t think my Gatorade matching my suit was a coincidence 💁🏼‍♀️) •••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••
Repost from @avpbeach

For the first time, we take you behind-the-scenes and in the coach's corner. Get an inside look at the coaching process and commentary of Olympic Silver Medalist and #AVP coach, @JenniferKessy, as she led the #ATeam into the Women's Final of the 2019 #AVPGoldSeries // Manhattan Beach Open.

node.text:
Getting ready for our last week of training at home before heading off to the OLYMPICS!🤯 My THIRD Olympics🤯🤯 I am so grateful and so excited! 🙌🏼

Rule 40 goes into effect on Tuesday so I won’t be able to show my love to certain partners while I’m in Tokyo, but if you’d like to support me and one of my longest standing sponsors you can purchase something from my ARxMizuno line🙏🏼 (the pieces I’m wearing in the photo plus more!) A little H&H camp update☀️😎💦

After a strong three days of heat and humidity training with @usavolleyball, plus weights, and including a match last night, this morning’s training GOT me 🥵😵‍💫 (thankfully I had my @gatorade to get me thru!🙌🏼) 

We have one more practice tm before we head home for the 4th 🤗🎇🇺🇸 and I want to feel ready for it so the rest of today is ALL about RECOVERY, that means Normatecing, napping, and nutrition- the 3 N’s of recovery as @dad_strength_podcast likes to say😂 plus some coffee and lots of reading of course!🧘🏼‍♀️

It was awesome seeing and training with @larissa_maestrini & @lili_maestrini this morning 👊🏼💪🏼 and can’t wait to go again with them tm!
